WEBVTT

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:36.680
Isn't Jiang Xinming the son of Jiang Yousan?

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:37.640
Mr. Du.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:39.240
I don't think my master

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:41.360
Would ever sell the Xuan family legacy

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:43.240
Off to Malaysia.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:50.520
Mr. Du.

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:54.560
Go back and tell your Mr. Jiang,

00:01:56.120 --> 00:02:00.720
Doing business requires integrity.

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:03.440
A person must be upright and honorable.

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:07.040
Only then can you go far.

00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:11.680
Uncle Xuan.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:14.840
Don't just stare at others' flaws

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.280
And ignore the scars on your own heels.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:19.960
Take a look at your own son Xuan Yi

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.720
And Chairman Xiao of the Xuan Paper Association.

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:24.640
See what kind of scheme they've cooked up.

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:29.960
They even hired this pretty lady to entertain.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.080
Quite a show!

00:02:34.440 --> 00:02:35.240
Let's go.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:37.560
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:48.080
You bastard!

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:48.720
Dad! Dad! Dad!

00:02:48.720 --> 00:02:49.400
Dad!

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.360
No, let me explain!

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.280
I'll beat you to death!

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:52.920
Old Xuan, have you lost your mind?

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:53.360
Mr. Xuan!

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:54.080
What are you doing?

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:54.840
Son!

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:57.800
Calm down!

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.160
Just let him beat me to death.

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:00.800
If I'm dead, his ancestors will be happy.

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:02.080
Mr. Xuan!

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:04.720
Why hit him so hard, Mr. Xuan?

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.720
Xuan Yi wasn't with Xiao Min to deceive you.

00:03:07.720 --> 00:03:09.800
They were truly afraid you'd sell the family treasure.

00:03:09.800 --> 00:03:11.840
They wanted to safeguard it for you!

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:12.600
Get out of the way!

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:13.920
Did you hear that?

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:16.280
Old Xuan, you're being foolish!

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:17.280
Mom, it's okay.

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:19.040
Come on, to the hospital, now.

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:19.440
I'm fine.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:19.880
Go.

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:20.760
Go on, go on, hurry up.

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:21.880
Mom, Mom, Mom.

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:24.000
Are we unable to pay wages again this month?

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:25.000
Don't worry about it.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:25.880
Xin Ran gave me my dividend,

00:03:25.880 --> 00:03:27.000
A hundred thousand yuan.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:29.080
I transferred it all to that same card.

00:03:29.160 --> 00:03:29.920
Everyone.

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.800
I'll have to ask for your patience this month.

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:33.240
We can only pay half the wages for now.

00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:34.720
I'll figure out the rest later.

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:35.520
You all know,

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:37.040
The Xuan family will never shortchange you.

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:37.560
Stop talking.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.200
Dad.

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:40.520
Whether traditional Xuan paper has a future,

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:41.920
You know best yourself.

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:44.240
Let's not argue. Arguing gets us nowhere.

00:03:44.920 --> 00:03:45.760
Hear me out.

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:47.280
Whether you think I'm right

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.360
Or wrong,

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:50.880
Since I'm a descendant of the Xuan family,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.800
I bear the responsibility

00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:54.680
To find a way forward for Xuan paper.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:03:59.480
Ignore him.

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:00.920
Hurry, to the hospital.

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:02.000
Come on, come on.

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:04.640
Don't let it leave a scar.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.040
Senior brother.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:11.520
Xuan Yi truly cares about the Xuan family.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.960
As for the wages,

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:14.280
Really, don't worry about it.

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:53.200
Made of Xuan paper.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.240
Of course.

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:55.960
In the near future,

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:58.680
I'll make everything here out of Xuan paper.

00:04:58.840 --> 00:04:59.800
Including this house.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.400
Houses can be made of Xuan paper too?

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.120
I've already tested it.

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.400
Strength and waterproofing are both fine.

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:07.680
Forget just building houses,

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.920
You could even build boats with it.

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:12.360
It sounds a bit unbelievable,

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.800
But somehow I think you can pull it off.

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:20.120
With ideas as wild as yours,

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:22.000
Just like you said,

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:24.360
Finding a new path for Xuan paper,

00:05:25.640 --> 00:05:27.520
All of this is just getting started.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:30.800
Come here.

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:47.240
Can you smell it?

00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:48.280
Smell what?

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:50.520
The scent of Xuan paper.

00:05:50.760 --> 00:05:53.160
I grew up smelling this scent,

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:55.640
Watching my parents make paper.

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:58.480
Back then, they were both young.

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:01.360
In my memory, Xuan paper was young too.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:02.840
Every generation of my ancestors

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:05.280
Looked just like my young parents.

00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:06.840
And the paper they made

00:06:07.320 --> 00:06:08.800
Was just like their skin,

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:11.480
Young, smooth, and glossy.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:15.640
But as my dad spoke less and less,

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.480
And his gray hairs grew,

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:19.520
And my mom smiled less,

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:23.080
The Xuan paper, along with them,

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:24.480
Suddenly grew old too.

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.000
And from that moment on,

00:06:28.520 --> 00:06:30.240
The ancestors in my imagination

00:06:30.320 --> 00:06:31.440
All grew old as well.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:32.880
By all rights,

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:35.120
In imagination, anything is possible.

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:36.400
You can do anything.

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.720
So why can't I

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:40.720
Make them young again?

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:45.400
So all the designs you're making now

00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:48.040
Are to make Xuan paper younger,

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.680
To bring Xuan paper and your family

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:52.840
Back to how they were in your childhood.

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:59.280
Our ancestors, through constant exploration,

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.920
Crafted the most exquisite Xuan paper.

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:04.360
So why can't we

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:06.840
Expand on the uses of Xuan paper

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:08.680
And breathe new life into it?

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:11.520
If you truly love Xuan paper,

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:13.240
You should let it move with the times,

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:15.520
Let it enter the young people's market,

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:17.480
Let it keep up with the trends,

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:19.520
To develop and grow.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:23.720
You really should let them hear all this,

00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:25.400
Especially your dad.

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:27.160
Forget it, no need.

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.520
He has his own shackles,

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:31.600
And his stubbornness too.

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:35.480
Best not let him know, then.

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:40.280
Careful, careful!

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:41.840
Why is it leaking?

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:44.240
No, this one failed.

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:46.160
No, it didn't fail.

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:50.520
It just needs a bit more refining.

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:07.720
Is this even Xuan paper?

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:10.360
Cutting corners, passing off shoddy goods.

00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:11.720
Notify the workshop.

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:12.720
Halt production immediately.

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:15.120
Manager Huang's point is,

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.680
Since the Xuans subcontracted the order,

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:19.920
On quality, shouldn't we be less...

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:21.400
The paper's from someone else,

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:23.320
But the finished product is Daya Studio's.

00:08:23.840 --> 00:08:25.040
Can we ruin our brand?

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:26.040
Halt production.

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.600
I'll order the shutdown right away.

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:29.400
Investigate where this batch came from.

00:08:30.360 --> 00:08:33.799
Three small family workshops are involved.

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:36.000
Hurry, go greet them.

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.240
Mr. Xin.

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:40.919
Yiran.

00:08:41.720 --> 00:08:42.159
Mr. Xin.

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:42.840
Secretary Peng.

00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:44.680
Look at you, look at you.

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:46.960
After your call, I didn't dare leave.

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:48.600
I've been waiting right here for you.

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:49.440
Come.

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:50.720
Secretary Peng.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:53.520
Look, our partnership just started,

00:08:53.520 --> 00:08:55.840
And already such a serious quality issue.

00:08:55.960 --> 00:08:58.040
Daya Studio will not tolerate this.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.600
Yes, rest assured.

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:02.360
We will not let this slide.

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:03.080
Good.

00:09:03.280 --> 00:09:04.120
Look at this.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:05.640
The leaders had just praised us,

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.680
And then this happens right after.

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:10.280
Luckily, your quality control is strict.

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:11.840
Otherwise, if word got out,

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:13.800
It'd be a slap in Taohua Town's face.

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:14.520
Yiran.

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:16.920
Take Mr. Xin to see Chairman Xiao.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:19.040
Tell him where we stand.

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:20.360
This must be handled severely.

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:23.160
Our Xuan Paper Association isn't for show.

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.680
When it's time to step up,

00:09:24.680 --> 00:09:26.160
It must step up.

00:09:26.400 --> 00:09:27.200
Understood.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.040
Well...

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:29.600
Mr. Xin, here's the thing.

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.720
I've got a county welfare inspection today.

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.840
I won't be able to accompany you.

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:34.800
Later, let me know the outcome

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:35.480
Of your discussion with Chairman Xiao.

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.480
If needed, I'll go see him myself.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:36.840
Okay.

00:09:36.840 --> 00:09:37.800
You two head off then.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:39.480
Let's go to the Xuan Paper Association.

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:47.360
Sorry about that.

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:48.640
Sorry, sorry.

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:50.000
Sorry to keep you both waiting.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:50.360
It's fine.

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:51.240
Please, have a seat.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.040
You see,

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.840
You didn't give me a heads-up.

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:54.840
I haven't even brewed any tea.

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:55.960
Let me pour you some water.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:57.600
Chairman Xiao, don't bother.

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.800
We're not here for tea.

00:09:58.800 --> 00:09:59.600
Let's get down to business.

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:00.920
Sit.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.240
Go ahead.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:07.800
Chairman Xiao,

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:10.160
Aren't you the responsible type?

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:13.040
When you came personally to win this order,

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:15.840
Didn't I make it clear at the time

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:17.240
That I was worried about quality control?

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:20.040
I said back then they couldn't deliver.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:21.800
And now it's come true, hasn't it?

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:22.840
Mr. Xin,

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.120
Right here.

00:10:24.400 --> 00:10:25.880
First, on behalf of them,

00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:29.720
I want to apologize to you and your company.

00:10:30.040 --> 00:10:32.800
We've smashed the pot before the meal began.

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:34.520
Of course, I bear responsibility too.

00:10:34.520 --> 00:10:35.440
Let's not talk about blame.

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:36.360
Let's talk about what to do.

00:10:36.360 --> 00:10:38.280
Secretary Peng's stance is very clear.

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:39.360
Handle it strictly.

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:40.560
I promise you,

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.720
It'll be handled strictly, no ambiguity.

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:43.640
Also,

00:10:43.640 --> 00:10:45.480
For losses caused to you and other clients,

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:47.080
I'll demand full compensation from them.

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.000
Not a single cent less.

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:48.760
Chairman Xiao,

00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:50.200
This isn't about compensation.

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:51.240
You need to understand,

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:53.040
Setting rules and industry standards

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:55.040
Is the only way to ensure healthy growth

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:55.880
Of Taohua Town's Xuan paper industry.

00:10:55.880 --> 00:10:57.360
You can't take a wishy-washy attitude.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.280
I suggest

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:01.520
Calling a meeting immediately to announce this.

00:11:01.520 --> 00:11:03.920
Then expel the factories with the worst quality

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:05.560
From the association.

00:11:05.560 --> 00:11:06.760
As for the other factories,

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:09.400
Penalize them according to severity.

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:12.560
Any similar orders the association gets in future

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:13.640
Will have nothing to do with them.

00:11:13.640 --> 00:11:16.560
Also, we redraft the industry charter,

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:18.080
And then all enterprises

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:19.800
Must sign the corresponding guarantees.

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:21.400
I agree with this resolution.

00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:23.400
Otherwise, situations like today

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.680
Will really be hard to change.

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.600
Look at me as chairman,

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:28.840
On the surface, all glamour and glory,

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:29.720
But in reality,

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:32.360
I'm like a maid catching grief from both sides.

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:34.000
Thankless work, that's what it is.

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:35.360
You have to understand,

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:37.480
All these years, I've taken my own orders

00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:38.960
And handed them out for them to make.

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:40.960
That's why they recognize me, Xiao Min,

00:11:40.960 --> 00:11:43.080
And are willing to call me chairman.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.960
If my association were a treasure trove,

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:46.960
That would be wonderful.

00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:48.600
Everyone could just dip in anytime.

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:50.240
I'd have piles of orders in hand,

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.600
Giving them to whomever I want,

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:53.120
Punishing whomever I want.

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.840
But that's not how things really are.

00:11:55.960 --> 00:11:57.720
Take this notebook order

00:11:57.720 --> 00:11:59.240
You just arranged, for example.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:00.880
The order isn't even that big.

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:03.200
If you punish them too harshly,

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:04.880
Or if this so-called

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:06.360
New industry code of yours

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:08.760
Doesn't consider those bosses' interests,

00:12:08.760 --> 00:12:10.760
They might get angry and impulsively

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:12.360
All quit the association.

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:14.360
By then, what good would

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.480
My association even be?

00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:17.600
How could I regulate the market then?

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:18.240
Right?

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:19.200
No, Chairman Xiao,

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:20.120
These are two different issues.

00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:22.200
We can't take a wishy-washy stance now.

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:23.720
I'm not being wishy-washy.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:26.240
If the industry can't grow or land orders,

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:29.120
Our Economic Development Office can help,

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:30.720
Working to make the industry stronger.

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:31.640
That's one matter.

00:12:31.640 --> 00:12:33.960
But failing to enforce due penalties

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:34.960
Is a second, separate matter.

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:37.200
Without clear rewards and punishments,

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:38.960
Managing Taohua Town's Xuan paper firms

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:40.000
Will just be a complete mess.

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.360
I believe real management

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:43.240
Must respect the industry's rules.

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:48.480
I'll report your views to Secretary Peng.

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:49.920
Chairman Xiao,

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:54.160
Speaking just on a personal level,

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:56.240
We truly understand your position

00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:58.760
As the head of the association.

00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:00.600
But we're truly sorry.

00:13:01.680 --> 00:13:02.920
We at Daya Studio

00:13:02.920 --> 00:13:04.680
Can't ruin our own reputation either.

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:06.760
Since you've already spoken your mind,

00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:09.080
I have no choice but to state my position.

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:10.200
Effective immediately,

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:11.600
All notebook business

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.720
Must be completely halted.

00:13:13.720 --> 00:13:14.480
Excuse me.

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:26.200
Even Confucius believed in

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:29.120
Teaching all without bias, by aptitude.

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.880
But with you, they're all beyond saving?

00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:33.200
You have to crush them all at once?

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:35.000
Save those words for your students.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:36.560
Doing this job is a different matter.

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:39.080
If you were my daughter, I'd...

00:13:39.080 --> 00:13:41.200
If these issues aren't handled strictly,

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:43.120
Those factories will follow suit,

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:44.560
Ruining themselves in the end.

00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:45.960
Lin Yiran,

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:48.320
What are you up to?

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:49.440
What am I up to?

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:50.720
Haven't you caused enough trouble?

00:13:50.840 --> 00:13:53.320
The association handles industry matters.

00:13:53.320 --> 00:13:54.640
Why are you sticking your nose in?

00:13:54.640 --> 00:13:56.120
They've come complaining to me.

00:13:56.360 --> 00:13:57.720
Like that serious mass incident

00:13:57.720 --> 00:13:58.480
That blew up last time.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:13:59.880
Why can't you learn your lesson?

00:13:59.880 --> 00:14:02.240
Should we do nothing for fear of trouble?

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:04.880
The town has a duty to guide and oversee

00:14:04.880 --> 00:14:06.600
The Xuan paper enterprises.

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:07.840
Our whole purpose

00:14:07.840 --> 00:14:10.560
Is the healthy growth of Xuan paper, right?

00:14:10.560 --> 00:14:11.960
So what did I do wrong?

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:14.040
Director Liao, look at this.

00:14:14.040 --> 00:14:14.640
This is your subordinate,

00:14:14.640 --> 00:14:15.440
Talking to me like this.

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:16.360
Don't you have a stance?

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:17.120
Don't you have any...

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:20.600
Yes, of course I have a stance.

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:22.160
Lin Yiran,

00:14:23.040 --> 00:14:23.840
Let's go.

00:14:25.640 --> 00:14:27.960
We'll visit the firms and solve this.

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:32.160
You...

00:14:32.760 --> 00:14:33.560
No, wait.

00:14:34.200 --> 00:14:35.840
I haven't finished yet.

00:14:37.200 --> 00:14:38.000
Actually,

00:14:38.360 --> 00:14:40.400
It's not that we have to

00:14:40.400 --> 00:14:42.880
Defend these small workshops and businesses,

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:46.480
But honestly, they really have it tough.

00:14:46.960 --> 00:14:48.440
Take labor costs, for example.

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.840
The wages they pay their workers

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:52.600
Have to be higher than ours.

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:53.760
Why?

00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.760
Because they're less stable than us.

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:57.960
And take raw materials.

00:14:58.480 --> 00:15:00.120
The wholesale price we get

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.720
Is definitely cheaper than theirs.

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:04.600
So what's the end result?

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:07.360
We put our heart into making for Daya Studio

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:08.480
And definitely turn a profit.

00:15:09.000 --> 00:15:11.120
But if they don't cut corners,

00:15:11.240 --> 00:15:12.840
They're definitely losing money.

00:15:13.240 --> 00:15:14.960
Times are this hard.

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:17.320
Who'd do business at a loss?

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:20.000
I understand the difficulties,

00:15:20.320 --> 00:15:21.480
But the logic doesn't hold.

00:15:22.080 --> 00:15:23.960
Cutting corners just because you're not making money

00:15:23.960 --> 00:15:25.080
Deserves sympathy?

00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:26.840
If you put it that way,

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:28.240
Restaurants that aren't profitable

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:30.240
Should use gutter oil and lymph meat?

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:32.240
Director Liao, let me tell you,

00:15:32.960 --> 00:15:34.480
The other day, Daya Studio

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:36.560
Wasn't happy with the paper we supplied.

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:38.560
They said our hand-scooped paper

00:15:38.600 --> 00:15:40.120
Had inconsistent quality

00:15:40.720 --> 00:15:41.840
And wanted to dock our pay.

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:43.840
I don't want this either,

00:15:44.480 --> 00:15:45.960
But the paper-scooping workers,

00:15:46.760 --> 00:15:48.560
They don't care how tight our schedule is.

00:15:49.120 --> 00:15:50.600
If they're unhappy,

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:52.440
Without so much as a word,

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:53.640
They just don't show up.

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:55.200
If they don't work for us,

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:57.080
They can go to other big factories.

00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:59.720
We can't even keep the staff stable.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:02.480
How do you expect me to keep quality stable?

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:05.840
Paper scoopers, paper dryers,

00:16:06.120 --> 00:16:09.480
That's what we call brutal work.

00:16:09.600 --> 00:16:11.600
In winter, scooping paper freezes you.

00:16:11.760 --> 00:16:14.200
In summer, drying paper roasts you.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:15.960
Young people these days

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:18.360
Would rather deliver food or drive rideshares.

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:22.640
They find it more comfortable and free.

00:16:22.720 --> 00:16:26.320
So fewer and fewer people do this work.

00:16:30.440 --> 00:16:31.360
Thank you, sir.

00:16:32.720 --> 00:16:34.160
No, no, don't say that.

00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:35.240
I'm not used to it.

00:16:37.640 --> 00:16:38.800
How can you carry this bag?

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:39.760
Come on, let me take it.

00:16:39.760 --> 00:16:42.120
No, no, I wouldn't dare trouble you.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:48.160
Last time, I really didn't mean it.

00:16:49.520 --> 00:16:51.240
Even unintentional, I can't take it.

00:16:51.320 --> 00:16:54.200
Let me treat you to local food for lunch.

00:16:54.400 --> 00:16:55.200
How about it?

00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:55.960
No need.

00:16:56.720 --> 00:16:58.520
Just give me some face.

00:16:59.120 --> 00:16:59.920
Can't do that.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.840
Even without eating your food, you raise hell.

00:17:02.960 --> 00:17:05.119
If I eat it, I'll be even more tongue-tied.

00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:07.319
No, the way you put it...

00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:09.960
Don't worry, I'll learn my lesson this time.

00:17:11.240 --> 00:17:12.359
I don't believe you.

00:17:12.480 --> 00:17:13.280
Lin Yiran,

00:17:14.280 --> 00:17:15.280
I, old Liao,

00:17:15.400 --> 00:17:18.200
Am cursed to have a subordinate like you.

00:17:18.560 --> 00:17:20.440
If you have any conscience left,

00:17:21.280 --> 00:17:22.839
Let me retire in peace.

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:25.000
That'd be doing me a great favor.

00:17:25.400 --> 00:17:26.599
No, Director Liao, I...

00:17:33.520 --> 00:17:34.280
Careful, careful, careful.

00:17:34.280 --> 00:17:35.120
Take it easy, Yingzi.

00:17:36.080 --> 00:17:36.680
Old Song.

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:38.440
Old Song.

00:17:40.120 --> 00:17:40.840
Director Liao.

00:17:41.320 --> 00:17:41.880
Xiao Lin.

00:17:41.880 --> 00:17:43.800
How can you let a kid do this work?

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:45.120
Come here, child.

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:47.600
Let me give you a hug.

00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:49.240
Director Liao, he's all dirty.

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:51.560
How old are you?

00:17:51.560 --> 00:17:52.360
Six.

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:53.760
Six years old.

00:17:53.960 --> 00:17:54.760
So young.

00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:56.720
Why is he already working?

00:17:57.120 --> 00:17:58.600
Have a seat, Director Liao.

00:17:59.720 --> 00:18:00.200
Please sit.

00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:00.600
Sit, sit, sit.

00:18:00.600 --> 00:18:01.560
I'll just stand for a bit.

00:18:01.560 --> 00:18:02.280
Director Liao.

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:03.720
Our business is small.

00:18:03.720 --> 00:18:06.200
We can't afford to hire help, so only family works here.

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:07.840
It's not easy.

00:18:09.120 --> 00:18:09.880
Old Song.

00:18:11.000 --> 00:18:13.160
For this Daya Studio paper order,

00:18:13.440 --> 00:18:15.280
Some shops cut corners.

00:18:16.120 --> 00:18:17.800
Why didn't you do the same?

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:18.680
We...

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:19.520
Teacher Liao.

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:22.160
You know what my dad's like.

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:23.880
Our family only makes authentic Xuan paper.

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:24.960
Right, right, right.

00:18:28.120 --> 00:18:29.720
With this notebook order,

00:18:30.120 --> 00:18:31.360
You should make a bit, right?

00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:34.120
It all went into raw materials.

00:18:34.880 --> 00:18:36.880
But luckily, the labor is our own.

00:18:36.960 --> 00:18:38.240
So we make a little something.

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:39.720
Just earning the labor cost.

00:18:42.680 --> 00:18:44.160
Have you graduated from high school?

00:18:44.920 --> 00:18:45.800
I'm a senior.

00:18:46.080 --> 00:18:48.280
That's exam-prep time, isn't it?

00:18:48.720 --> 00:18:50.000
The family's too busy.

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:52.560
My sister and I help out at home.

00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:55.560
Such a thoughtful kid.

00:18:56.720 --> 00:18:57.560
Youbu.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.000
Old Song.

00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:04.200
How much is sandalwood bark pulp per ton?

00:19:05.040 --> 00:19:06.080
About 150,000.

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:10.720
Small workshops like theirs

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:12.280
Don't have the means to process pulp.

00:19:12.280 --> 00:19:14.520
They can only buy it from outside.

00:19:14.920 --> 00:19:15.760
Right.

00:19:16.640 --> 00:19:20.560
Director Liao, Chairman Xiao buys the best pulp,

00:19:20.640 --> 00:19:21.720
140,000 per ton.

00:19:22.320 --> 00:19:23.840
I'm paying up to 170,000.

00:19:23.840 --> 00:19:25.680
And my quality still isn't as good as his.

00:19:26.560 --> 00:19:28.080
I'm just glad I can buy any at all.

00:19:28.080 --> 00:19:29.760
When raw materials are tight,

00:19:29.760 --> 00:19:31.080
They won't even sell to you.

00:19:31.200 --> 00:19:32.120
Right, right, right.

00:19:33.040 --> 00:19:34.360
This is the township's order,

00:19:34.760 --> 00:19:36.360
And Daya Studio is a big company.

00:19:36.360 --> 00:19:38.120
I can't slack on quality.

00:19:38.120 --> 00:19:39.360
I'd rather make no money

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:41.560
Than ruin our own brand, right?

00:19:42.080 --> 00:19:46.080
Always making no money isn't a solution either.

00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:49.800
Director Liao.

00:19:51.080 --> 00:19:52.560
Chairman Xiao.

00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:53.040
Uncle Xiao.

00:19:53.040 --> 00:19:54.040
What brings you here?

00:19:54.520 --> 00:19:57.160
I heard you and Comrade Xiao Lin

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:58.360
Were touring the workshops.

00:19:58.360 --> 00:19:59.080
So I came to take a look.

00:19:59.080 --> 00:20:01.800
I'm with Xiao Lin, doing an incognito visit.

00:20:01.800 --> 00:20:03.840
What a fine incognito visit you're doing.

00:20:03.840 --> 00:20:05.920
You should take her to survey local conditions.

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:07.840
Comrade Xiao Lin,

00:20:08.520 --> 00:20:09.760
How's the survey going?

00:20:10.120 --> 00:20:10.920
Pretty good.

00:20:12.120 --> 00:20:12.880
Here, Yingzi.

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:14.000
This is for you.

00:20:14.040 --> 00:20:14.840
Thank you, Uncle Xiao.

00:20:14.840 --> 00:20:16.120
Get yourself some good nutrition.

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:17.880
This is for the old man.

00:20:18.360 --> 00:20:19.560
Pastries, nice and soft.

00:20:19.560 --> 00:20:20.560
You're too kind, Chairman Xiao.

00:20:20.560 --> 00:20:21.240
Thank you, thank you.

00:20:21.240 --> 00:20:22.280
It's nothing, nothing. Sister-in-law.

00:20:24.160 --> 00:20:25.080
How's the studying going?

00:20:25.120 --> 00:20:25.840
Not bad.

00:20:25.840 --> 00:20:26.640
Do well on the exam.

00:20:27.360 --> 00:20:28.160
Director Liao.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:29.400
Let me tell you something.

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:31.200
Chairman Xiao treats us small business owners

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:32.600
With extraordinary care.

00:20:32.600 --> 00:20:34.840
Any association member's kid who gets into college

00:20:34.840 --> 00:20:35.880
Gets a reward.

00:20:35.880 --> 00:20:38.120
Five thousand for a regular university.

00:20:38.320 --> 00:20:40.520
Ten thousand for a top one.

00:20:40.600 --> 00:20:41.440
Never mind that.

00:20:42.440 --> 00:20:43.840
The association has such a policy?

00:20:43.840 --> 00:20:45.320
I... I set it up.

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:46.880
All the kids of association members

00:20:46.880 --> 00:20:47.840
Are treated equally.

00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:49.520
The membership fees, right?

00:20:49.600 --> 00:20:51.600
They're just sitting there anyway.

00:20:51.600 --> 00:20:53.040
Better to spend them on the kids.

00:20:53.840 --> 00:20:56.160
The association collects that much in fees?

00:20:57.160 --> 00:20:58.000
Yes, yes, yes.

00:20:58.080 --> 00:20:59.760
With so many big and small businesses,

00:20:59.840 --> 00:21:02.320
Plus some government support,

00:21:02.320 --> 00:21:02.760
You know.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:04.800
Chairman Xiao.

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:07.720
My attitude towards you earlier was wrong.

00:21:07.880 --> 00:21:09.960
I owe you an apology.

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:11.360
It's fine, it's fine.

00:21:11.760 --> 00:21:13.880
I was a bit worked up that day too.

00:21:14.360 --> 00:21:15.440
Everyone meant well.

00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:16.600
We just need to understand each other.

00:21:16.640 --> 00:21:18.000
But regardless,

00:21:18.120 --> 00:21:20.320
The current situation has to change.

00:21:21.120 --> 00:21:22.760
So what you mean is...

00:21:23.480 --> 00:21:25.280
For this cutting-corners penalty,

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:27.120
Let's just do as you suggested.

00:21:27.320 --> 00:21:29.080
Compensate Daya Studio for the losses,

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:31.800
Ban them from association orders for a year,

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.720
And have them pledge never to do it again.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:35.520
Does that sound okay?

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:36.560
Sure.

00:21:36.760 --> 00:21:38.000
I guarantee there'll be no problem.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:40.000
Penalties must be enforced.

00:21:40.280 --> 00:21:41.200
That's the right call.

00:21:41.320 --> 00:21:42.040
But you know,

00:21:43.160 --> 00:21:46.560
Honest folks like the Song family,

00:21:47.200 --> 00:21:49.120
Small factories with real difficulties,

00:21:49.640 --> 00:21:51.600
We should help them out too.

00:21:52.040 --> 00:21:52.880
Director Liao,

00:21:53.320 --> 00:21:55.080
Let me handle this matter.

00:21:55.480 --> 00:21:58.120
Material supply isn't too tight this year.

00:21:58.560 --> 00:22:00.640
I'll order a few dozen extra tons,

00:22:01.040 --> 00:22:03.320
Then distribute them to small firms at cost.

00:22:04.120 --> 00:22:07.000
You're truly a worthy chairman.

00:22:07.880 --> 00:22:08.680
Chairman Xiao.

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:10.760
Drop me off at Daya Studio in a bit.

00:22:10.760 --> 00:22:12.480
I'll have another talk with Xin Ran.

00:22:12.600 --> 00:22:13.840
Ask her to be more understanding.

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:16.520
After all, we have to keep working together.

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:18.440
Okay, thanks for your trouble.

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:19.560
It's the least I can do.

00:22:19.800 --> 00:22:21.200
Also invite her and Xuan Yi along.

00:22:21.360 --> 00:22:22.560
Let's get together tonight.

00:22:23.360 --> 00:22:25.280
My dad said you single-handedly

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:27.360
Started a big company in Taohua Town.

00:22:27.760 --> 00:22:29.200
That's so impressive.

00:22:29.360 --> 00:22:31.680
I want to be just like you when I grow up.

00:22:33.120 --> 00:22:35.920
You might turn out even better than me.

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:38.600
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:43.800
The lyrics really moved me.

00:22:46.800 --> 00:22:48.680
"I wish, when you're lonely,

00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:50.880
I could be there with you."

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:55.920
"When you're lonely, who do you think of?"

00:22:56.080 --> 00:22:56.680
None of your business.

00:22:56.680 --> 00:22:58.280
"When you're sad, I'll comfort you."

00:23:01.480 --> 00:23:01.920
I really want to...

00:23:01.920 --> 00:23:03.160
Stop sighing, Chairman Xiao.

00:23:04.040 --> 00:23:05.600
Today, I want to thank you.

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:06.840
Really, I'm so happy.

00:23:06.840 --> 00:23:07.120
Cheers!

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:07.840
No, no, no.

00:23:08.200 --> 00:23:10.560
If anyone should thank, it's me thanking you.

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:12.000
For making your Daya Studio

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:12.880
Suffer such a huge loss.

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:16.120
Chairman Xiao, we're off the clock.

00:23:16.360 --> 00:23:17.840
Can't we just enjoy ourselves?

00:23:19.600 --> 00:23:20.120
Alright.

00:23:20.120 --> 00:23:20.840
Cheers.

00:23:21.040 --> 00:23:21.840
Thank you.

00:23:22.360 --> 00:23:23.160
Come on!

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:24.440
Taking this occasion,

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:26.120
I want to share something with you all.

00:23:26.840 --> 00:23:28.080
I'm heading back to Beijing.

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:30.000
What for?

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:31.760
To bring back orders.

00:23:31.760 --> 00:23:33.800
I'll reach out to old colleagues and friends.

00:23:33.800 --> 00:23:34.600
Try to figure something out.

00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:35.680
See if there's a chance

00:23:35.680 --> 00:23:38.120
To grow the Xuan paper industry bigger.

00:23:38.360 --> 00:23:39.880
Make sure everyone has work,

00:23:39.880 --> 00:23:41.160
And plenty of it.

00:23:42.840 --> 00:23:44.760
I'm noticing you really love

00:23:44.800 --> 00:23:46.320
Acting on every whim.

00:23:46.360 --> 00:23:48.600
Bold and daring, a real fighter, you are.

00:23:49.840 --> 00:23:51.120
I want to give it a shot.

00:23:51.560 --> 00:23:54.560
Even if it just eases our current bind,

00:23:54.760 --> 00:23:56.680
That's better than doing nothing, right?

00:23:57.120 --> 00:23:58.760
If I bring back more orders,

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:01.400
We can finalize the industry standards.

00:24:01.560 --> 00:24:03.360
Then our Xuan paper industry

00:24:03.360 --> 00:24:04.800
Will get on the right track.

00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:06.080
I'm in.

00:24:06.840 --> 00:24:08.400
Yiran's awesome as always.

00:24:08.560 --> 00:24:10.040
Fortune favors the bold.

00:24:10.800 --> 00:24:11.680
Cheers!

00:24:12.560 --> 00:24:13.160
Let's jump!

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:13.760
Slow down.

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:14.920
One, two!

00:24:17.120 --> 00:24:17.680
Xiao Min!

00:24:17.800 --> 00:24:19.280
Run, run, run!

00:24:19.960 --> 00:24:20.840
Wait up!

00:24:20.840 --> 00:24:22.160
Chairman Xiao, you...

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:25.120
Don't get the kid wet, Xiao Min!

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:27.600
Lin Yiran!

00:24:28.080 --> 00:24:31.440
May your Beijing trip go smoothly.

00:24:32.720 --> 00:24:34.440
Xuan Yi, you just wait!

00:24:34.440 --> 00:24:35.360
Wait till I get back.

00:24:38.160 --> 00:24:40.360
Lin Yiran, you're going to Beijing alone,

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:42.200
So why do we all have to get soaked?

00:24:43.280 --> 00:24:44.360
My bad, sis!

00:24:44.440 --> 00:24:45.440
Don't run away, Lin Yiran!

00:24:45.440 --> 00:24:46.840
What were you chatting about with Aunt Xin?

00:24:46.920 --> 00:24:49.040
Not telling. It's our secret.

00:24:50.320 --> 00:24:52.200
Aunt Xin Ran seems to really like you.

00:24:52.480 --> 00:24:54.600
Your EQ is higher than your dad's, kid.

00:24:55.720 --> 00:24:56.920
Because I'm kind.

00:24:58.120 --> 00:24:58.920
You're what?

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:00.840
A scallop.

00:25:01.400 --> 00:25:02.400
Why are you so out of touch?

00:25:02.400 --> 00:25:04.080
It's a meme, a meme!

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:05.400
Aunt Xin.

00:25:05.720 --> 00:25:06.880
You're the out-of-touch one.

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:08.000
Slow down.

00:25:19.200 --> 00:25:20.120
So, tell me.

00:25:20.360 --> 00:25:22.760
Mr. Lin, top salesman for Taohua Town's Xuan paper.

00:25:23.360 --> 00:25:24.120
Don't even mention it.

00:25:24.120 --> 00:25:25.600
I haven't even started selling yet.

00:25:26.040 --> 00:25:27.520
I'm not trying to rain on your parade,

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:29.520
But trying or not probably won't make much difference.

00:25:29.840 --> 00:25:31.600
I asked everyone around me today,

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:33.600
And everyone's reaction was the same.

00:25:34.080 --> 00:25:36.600
"Xuan paper? Heard of it, never used it."

00:25:36.600 --> 00:25:39.120
"Our offices are all paperless now."

00:25:39.800 --> 00:25:41.120
So that's why I say,

00:25:41.320 --> 00:25:43.520
You don't deserve to use Xuan paper.

00:25:43.920 --> 00:25:45.440
It really is a fine product,

00:25:45.600 --> 00:25:46.800
But it's outdated.

00:25:47.360 --> 00:25:48.280
This time around,

00:25:48.640 --> 00:25:50.680
I'm afraid you've grabbed a hot potato.

00:25:53.200 --> 00:25:55.440
The countryside is a vast world of opportunity.

00:25:56.080 --> 00:25:58.360
I support you working there.

00:25:58.840 --> 00:26:01.360
But my ability is limited.

00:26:01.840 --> 00:26:03.120
I made a round of calls,

00:26:03.280 --> 00:26:06.040
Asked all my old colleagues and friends,

00:26:06.320 --> 00:26:08.840
And only managed to get a tiny order.

00:26:09.280 --> 00:26:11.120
It's hardly worth mentioning.

00:26:11.120 --> 00:26:12.880
No, professor, please don't say that.

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:14.000
I just got to Beijing,

00:26:14.000 --> 00:26:15.440
And you've already given me a great start.

00:26:15.440 --> 00:26:16.840
I don't even know how to thank you.

00:26:18.320 --> 00:26:19.840
I came from the countryside myself.

00:26:20.520 --> 00:26:21.920
You doing a good job out there

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:24.840
Is the greatest thanks you can give me.

00:26:27.840 --> 00:26:28.360
Let's go.

00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:35.120
Sister Qu,

00:26:36.480 --> 00:26:37.560
Yes, it's me, Yiran.

00:26:37.720 --> 00:26:38.800
I'm back in Beijing this time,

00:26:38.800 --> 00:26:40.480
And I was thinking of paying you a visit.

00:26:44.120 --> 00:26:44.840
It's fine, it's fine.

00:26:44.840 --> 00:26:46.880
It really was too sudden. No worries.

00:26:47.080 --> 00:26:48.120
Let's do it another day, then.

00:27:08.160 --> 00:27:09.600
I'm exhausted.

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:15.600
One look at you and I know how it went.

00:27:18.560 --> 00:27:19.680
There's something

00:27:20.120 --> 00:27:21.920
I've been debating whether to tell you.

00:27:21.920 --> 00:27:23.200
Don't hesitate, just say it.

00:27:23.440 --> 00:27:24.640
It can't get any worse than this.

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:25.840
Just come out with it.

00:27:27.120 --> 00:27:28.320
Emma is now at the company,

00:27:28.320 --> 00:27:29.920
In charge of the art division.

00:28:00.680 --> 00:28:01.320
Emma.

00:28:03.560 --> 00:28:04.160
Yiran.

00:28:05.280 --> 00:28:07.360
Lisa mentioned you out of the blue yesterday.

00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:08.360
I knew it.

00:28:08.360 --> 00:28:09.640
You'd come back begging me.

00:28:11.600 --> 00:28:12.840
Iced Americano, half sugar.

00:28:14.120 --> 00:28:15.920
Do you wait on bosses like this over there too?

00:28:16.600 --> 00:28:17.560
Do bosses in the mountains

00:28:17.560 --> 00:28:18.800
Even drink coffee?

00:28:24.760 --> 00:28:27.400
There are plenty of trendy cafes in the mountains.

00:28:27.640 --> 00:28:28.640
But over there,

00:28:28.840 --> 00:28:30.360
We also produce a lot of fine green tea.

00:28:30.600 --> 00:28:32.040
We're more used to drinking tea.

00:28:32.800 --> 00:28:33.480
Besides,

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:35.000
The leaders over there

00:28:35.440 --> 00:28:36.360
Don't need anyone waiting on them.

00:28:37.280 --> 00:28:40.320
I've always liked your attitude—neither servile nor arrogant.

00:28:40.480 --> 00:28:41.080
So confident.

00:28:41.560 --> 00:28:42.240
And self-respecting.

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:44.600
That's why I had such high hopes for you.

00:28:44.600 --> 00:28:46.280
And put real effort into mentoring you.

00:28:46.800 --> 00:28:48.080
You really let me down.

00:28:48.360 --> 00:28:49.960
Throwing away a bright future here,

00:28:50.120 --> 00:28:52.240
Running off to be a civil servant in some town.

00:28:53.120 --> 00:28:53.840
This time you're back,

00:28:54.240 --> 00:28:55.560
You're not going to disappoint me again, are you?

00:28:56.040 --> 00:28:57.800
I'm not here looking for a job this time.

00:28:58.200 --> 00:28:59.600
I'm here to ask you for a favor.

00:29:00.040 --> 00:29:01.040
To find a sales channel

00:29:01.560 --> 00:29:02.440
For Xuan paper.

00:29:03.080 --> 00:29:04.360
So the civil servant

00:29:04.600 --> 00:29:06.440
Has turned into a salesperson.

00:29:07.160 --> 00:29:08.040
It's for work.

00:29:08.400 --> 00:29:09.440
The title doesn't matter.

00:29:09.760 --> 00:29:11.440
You don't work for me anymore.

00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:13.120
Why should I help you?

00:29:23.560 --> 00:29:24.160
Yiran.

00:29:26.640 --> 00:29:28.840
It's been ages since we last met.

00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:29.920
How have things been going

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:31.440
For you back in your hometown?

00:29:31.600 --> 00:29:32.440
Not bad.

00:29:33.400 --> 00:29:34.400
I've heard

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:36.040
Your hometown has been built up beautifully.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:37.800
It's pretty nice.

00:29:37.800 --> 00:29:38.520
What's the situation right now?

00:29:38.720 --> 00:29:41.040
The wallpaper shipped from Italy hit a hurricane.

00:29:41.280 --> 00:29:42.720
The delivery has been delayed.

00:29:43.120 --> 00:29:44.040
Does Riccardo know yet?

00:29:44.120 --> 00:29:45.440
He's already at the site.

00:29:45.600 --> 00:29:47.200
But I hear he's furious.

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:48.120
Yelling at everyone.

00:29:48.520 --> 00:29:49.840
Sea shipping is usually so reliable.

00:29:49.840 --> 00:29:51.120
What the hell happened today?

00:29:58.560 --> 00:29:59.120
Emma.

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:01.440
Emma.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:03.160
Let me come with you.

00:30:03.520 --> 00:30:05.400
I've organized an exhibition for Riccardo before.

00:30:05.520 --> 00:30:06.600
I know how to handle him.

00:30:18.960 --> 00:30:20.240
Hello, Riccardo.

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:27.760
Mr. Riccardo.

00:30:27.800 --> 00:30:29.240
Emma, look what you've done.

00:30:30.840 --> 00:30:32.680
Riccardo, I'll figure something out right away.

00:30:32.760 --> 00:30:33.960
What can you possibly do?

00:30:33.960 --> 00:30:35.280
What solution could you have?

00:30:35.280 --> 00:30:36.520
There's only that much wallpaper.

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:37.760
And it's stuck out at sea now.

00:30:37.760 --> 00:30:40.040
Are you sending a helicopter to fetch it?

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:41.760
We'll reship it by air.

00:30:41.840 --> 00:30:44.040
My custom wallpaper had a limited production run.

00:30:44.040 --> 00:30:45.200
There isn't any more.

00:30:45.200 --> 00:30:46.600
And it's stranded at sea.

00:30:46.720 --> 00:30:48.160
How am I supposed to present my show?

00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:49.960
I told you.

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:51.520
I said ship it by air. So where is it?

00:30:51.520 --> 00:30:52.800
Why didn't you listen?

00:30:53.240 --> 00:30:54.720
There would've been enough time.

00:30:54.720 --> 00:30:56.720
But the cargo ship hit a hurricane.

00:30:56.720 --> 00:30:57.520
It was an accident.

00:30:57.520 --> 00:30:58.680
I don't care about excuses.

00:30:59.480 --> 00:31:00.240
Emma.

00:31:01.040 --> 00:31:03.640
How about we contact ships near the coast?

00:31:03.640 --> 00:31:04.840
And there are ports nearby too.

00:31:05.600 --> 00:31:06.960
Did you leave your brain at home?

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:09.040
I told you, it's a hurricane! How could anyone fetch it?

00:31:10.240 --> 00:31:12.880
Emma, you've ruined my exhibition.

00:31:12.880 --> 00:31:15.320
You breached the contract. You're responsible.

00:31:16.600 --> 00:31:18.400
Riccardo, let me explain.

00:31:27.240 --> 00:31:28.320
I'm new here.

00:31:28.320 --> 00:31:30.240
I'm just not capable enough.

00:31:30.720 --> 00:31:31.800
I didn't do my job well.

00:31:32.240 --> 00:31:34.360
I haven't adapted to Emma's work style yet.

00:31:36.640 --> 00:31:37.440
I heard

00:31:38.520 --> 00:31:40.720
You used to be Emma's favorite assistant.

00:31:41.800 --> 00:31:42.760
That's all in the past.

00:31:43.480 --> 00:31:46.240
Just focus on helping her solve the problem.

00:31:46.400 --> 00:31:48.440
Don't take her attitude to heart.

00:31:51.720 --> 00:31:53.640
Let's exchange contact info.

00:31:53.760 --> 00:31:55.400
You can send me Riccardo's

00:31:55.400 --> 00:31:56.360
Design proposal too.

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:00.320
Lin Yiran.

00:32:02.280 --> 00:32:03.080
Hello.

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:04.040
What's up?

00:32:04.280 --> 00:32:07.600
Can Xuan paper achieve a wallpaper effect?

00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:08.760
Others can't.

00:32:09.160 --> 00:32:10.520
I'm asking you.

00:32:10.760 --> 00:32:11.920
I can do anything.

00:32:13.080 --> 00:32:14.240
I'm being serious here.

00:32:14.720 --> 00:32:17.000
Riccardo's interior design exhibition

00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:19.480
Urgently needs an alternative wallpaper material.

00:32:19.480 --> 00:32:20.240
So I'll

00:32:20.280 --> 00:32:22.600
Send you his design drafts now.

00:32:22.600 --> 00:32:24.680
Follow his design concept

00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:26.160
And recreate it with Xuan paper.

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:27.240
This is really important.

00:32:27.320 --> 00:32:28.200
Riccardo, right?

00:32:28.200 --> 00:32:30.280
The world-famous interior designer?

00:32:31.320 --> 00:32:32.120
Yes.

00:32:32.320 --> 00:32:33.720
And at this exhibition,

00:32:33.720 --> 00:32:35.760
Many Chinese designers

00:32:35.840 --> 00:32:37.920
Will look to Riccardo's work for inspiration.

00:32:38.120 --> 00:32:40.960
If he accepts the Xuan paper plan,

00:32:40.960 --> 00:32:43.200
Plenty of Chinese designers

00:32:43.200 --> 00:32:44.480
Will imitate and follow suit.

00:32:44.760 --> 00:32:45.560
That way,

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:47.840
Xuan paper wallpaper could very well

00:32:47.840 --> 00:32:49.920
Carve out a niche in China's

00:32:49.920 --> 00:32:51.040
High-end interior design industry.

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.960
It could even become a trend.

00:32:54.840 --> 00:32:55.600
Alright.

00:32:55.600 --> 00:32:56.280
Here's the deal.

00:32:56.320 --> 00:32:58.160
Bring me a roast duck when you come.

00:32:58.160 --> 00:33:00.080
Not vacuum-packed. I want it freshly roasted.

00:33:00.080 --> 00:33:02.000
Buy it right before you board the train.

00:33:02.120 --> 00:33:03.800
I'm talking business here.

00:33:03.800 --> 00:33:06.040
This design determines your success or failure.

00:33:06.240 --> 00:33:07.360
What I said is also business.

00:33:07.360 --> 00:33:08.720
I'll deliver your wallpaper

00:33:08.800 --> 00:33:10.440
With guaranteed quality and quantity.

00:33:10.440 --> 00:33:12.880
And you'd better bring me that roast duck the same way.

00:33:13.800 --> 00:33:14.640
You really want to eat it?

00:33:15.440 --> 00:33:16.880
I really love roast duck.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:18.320
Why don't you just eat yourself?

00:33:19.520 --> 00:33:20.320
Fine, hanging up.

00:33:26.600 --> 00:33:30.080
We'll make this batch as premium bark paper.

00:33:30.560 --> 00:33:31.840
Eighty percent sandalwood bark.

00:33:31.840 --> 00:33:33.480
Twenty percent rice straw.

00:33:33.600 --> 00:33:34.600
The pulping is the key step.

00:33:35.000 --> 00:33:37.680
Uncle Hu and Zhang Du,

00:33:37.760 --> 00:33:38.920
The two of you will handle this part.

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:39.760
Got it.

00:33:40.200 --> 00:33:42.040
Uncle Ye, you'll handle the screen.

00:33:42.040 --> 00:33:44.000
Your son Ma Gan'er can lift the screen with you.

00:33:44.080 --> 00:33:46.680
Remember, scoop three-layer Xuan paper.

00:33:46.720 --> 00:33:48.840
No problem. Three-layer Xuan it is.

00:33:49.800 --> 00:33:50.600
Auntie Sulan,

00:33:50.680 --> 00:33:52.960
You take Xiao Yu and Xiao Man to brush the paper.

00:33:53.080 --> 00:33:53.880
Sure thing.

00:33:54.920 --> 00:33:55.720
Xuan Yi.

00:33:56.320 --> 00:33:57.520
What should I do?

00:33:58.680 --> 00:33:59.480
Uncle,

00:34:00.200 --> 00:34:01.840
We've got enough hands here already.

00:34:01.840 --> 00:34:02.400
And besides,

00:34:02.400 --> 00:34:04.160
We're definitely pulling an all-nighter today.

00:34:04.160 --> 00:34:05.520
You're not as young as you used to be.

00:34:05.600 --> 00:34:06.760
I don't want you wearing yourself out.

00:34:06.760 --> 00:34:07.840
Just get some rest early.

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:09.000
I can handle it.

00:34:09.239 --> 00:34:10.000
Yes, yes, yes.

00:34:10.000 --> 00:34:11.000
You've got us.

00:34:11.000 --> 00:34:11.600
Take it easy.

00:34:11.600 --> 00:34:12.280
That's right.

00:34:12.920 --> 00:34:14.320
I'll just take care of everyone

00:34:14.320 --> 00:34:15.560
By making a nice late-night meal.

00:34:15.560 --> 00:34:18.440
I'll get the duck soup simmering soon.

00:34:19.000 --> 00:34:19.760
Thank you, Auntie.

00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:21.159
No one knows a son like his mother.

00:34:21.600 --> 00:34:23.239
Alright, everyone clear on this?

00:34:23.239 --> 00:34:23.920
Got it.

00:34:23.920 --> 00:34:24.520
Good.

00:34:24.760 --> 00:34:26.280
Time's tight and the task is heavy.

00:34:26.719 --> 00:34:27.760
Enough talk.

00:34:27.760 --> 00:34:28.440
Let's get to work!

00:36:07.680 --> 00:36:08.600
Xuan Yi.

00:36:09.320 --> 00:36:11.840
Which of these colors will work?

00:36:17.920 --> 00:36:18.680
Auntie Sulan.

00:36:19.200 --> 00:36:21.520
This color is pretty close.

00:36:22.320 --> 00:36:24.000
Is this the color we're printing now?

00:36:24.000 --> 00:36:25.160
Yes, this one.

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:28.920
Silly me.

00:36:29.200 --> 00:36:30.520
I just mixed a new batch.

00:36:30.520 --> 00:36:31.440
We'll try again in a bit.

00:36:31.600 --> 00:36:32.520
Okay, okay.

00:36:32.840 --> 00:36:34.960
Xiao Yu, try another one.

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:37.480
Thanks for the hard work, everyone.

00:36:37.480 --> 00:36:38.240
No problem.

00:36:39.440 --> 00:36:40.200
Come on.

00:36:47.640 --> 00:36:50.000
Rachel, what's going on?

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:52.200
Wasn't Emma's meeting with Riccardo the day after tomorrow?

00:36:52.600 --> 00:36:54.000
Riccardo changed his schedule.

00:36:54.000 --> 00:36:55.400
He's not going to Shanghai.

00:36:55.520 --> 00:36:56.360
This morning when he got up,

00:36:56.360 --> 00:36:57.800
He called Emma.

00:36:57.840 --> 00:37:00.040
He said after wrapping up some final matters,

00:37:00.040 --> 00:37:01.520
He's flying straight back to Italy.

00:37:01.680 --> 00:37:03.360
How are we supposed to make it in time?

00:37:03.640 --> 00:37:04.880
The paper is already done.

00:37:04.880 --> 00:37:06.360
We sent it by air express this morning.

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:07.480
Even rushed,

00:37:07.520 --> 00:37:09.440
The earliest it can arrive is tomorrow morning.

00:37:10.000 --> 00:37:11.120
How will that be in time?

00:37:11.120 --> 00:37:12.120
What do we do?

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:14.600
Don't panic. Let me make a call.

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:17.600
The fusion of Chinese Xuan paper and Italian design

00:37:17.720 --> 00:37:20.280
Isn't just grafting two materials together.

00:37:20.320 --> 00:37:22.640
It's a spiritual resonance between two cultures.

00:37:22.960 --> 00:37:24.440
Imagine this:

00:37:24.520 --> 00:37:27.600
Translucent paper pulp projecting onto the walls

00:37:27.600 --> 00:37:29.520
The ink-wash breath of a landscape painting.

00:37:29.840 --> 00:37:31.000
What this collision creates

00:37:31.000 --> 00:37:33.040
Isn't just simple Chinese-style design.

00:37:33.040 --> 00:37:34.440
It's more akin to

00:37:34.440 --> 00:37:36.680
The precise structure of

00:37:36.680 --> 00:37:37.560
The Florence Cathedral's dome.

00:37:37.720 --> 00:37:40.320
Eastern softness becomes the aesthetic foundation

00:37:40.320 --> 00:37:41.200
Supporting Western strength.

00:37:41.200 --> 00:37:43.920
It's a revolutionary breakthrough in poetics and visuals.

00:37:44.920 --> 00:37:45.960
Mr. Riccardo,

00:37:46.160 --> 00:37:48.280
None of the parameters have changed.

00:37:48.280 --> 00:37:49.840
The only change is the material,

00:37:49.840 --> 00:37:51.480
From hemp to Xuan paper.

00:37:51.480 --> 00:37:52.000
I...

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:54.400
If all you're giving me is this pitch,

00:37:54.480 --> 00:37:55.920
Then I'm deeply disappointed.

00:37:56.000 --> 00:37:57.320
I want to see the finished product.

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:59.520
The finished product, right in front of me.

00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:01.400
Otherwise, I won't do this job.

00:38:01.400 --> 00:38:02.040
No, no, no.

00:38:02.040 --> 00:38:04.040
The finished piece is already on its way to Beijing.

00:38:04.040 --> 00:38:04.720
I...

00:38:04.840 --> 00:38:06.520
I don't believe any of this.

00:38:06.680 --> 00:38:07.840
I'm an artist.

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:11.000
My work cannot suffer the slightest compromise.

00:38:11.280 --> 00:38:12.400
Otherwise, I'm out.

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:13.520
You'll foot the bill yourselves.

00:38:16.800 --> 00:38:17.600
Hey.

00:38:17.800 --> 00:38:18.560
Got to say,

00:38:18.560 --> 00:38:20.120
This foreigner sure knows how to pick a spot.

00:38:20.720 --> 00:38:21.680
Where are you?

00:38:21.680 --> 00:38:23.680
Are you on the boat or off the boat?

00:38:23.800 --> 00:38:25.120
You didn't even come to greet me.

00:38:26.720 --> 00:38:27.520
Xuan Yi.

00:38:41.760 --> 00:38:42.560
Please.

00:38:47.880 --> 00:38:49.600
I was worried the courier wouldn't make it,

00:38:49.600 --> 00:38:51.280
So I caught the early morning flight

00:38:51.280 --> 00:38:52.920
And brought it to you in person.

00:38:52.920 --> 00:38:54.000
How's that? Reliable, right?

00:38:54.040 --> 00:38:54.920
Early morning flight?

00:38:55.880 --> 00:38:57.360
It's already afternoon.

00:38:58.320 --> 00:39:00.280
There's a roast duck place near the exhibition hall.

00:39:01.040 --> 00:39:01.960
Tastes great.

00:39:04.360 --> 00:39:05.240
You're really something.

00:39:08.280 --> 00:39:09.320
Who made this?

00:39:10.040 --> 00:39:10.960
This person right here.

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:12.560
Born into a Xuan paper family.

00:39:12.560 --> 00:39:13.440
Just like you,

00:39:13.440 --> 00:39:15.360
An extremely talented designer.

00:39:17.320 --> 00:39:18.880
This is incredible.

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:21.800
I see the sky-blue of Emperor Huizong.

00:39:22.200 --> 00:39:23.720
Magical Xuan paper.

00:39:23.880 --> 00:39:25.440
Magical designer.

00:39:26.200 --> 00:39:28.720
This is definitely the best choice right now.

00:39:29.200 --> 00:39:31.880
As for the actual effect, on opening day,

00:39:31.880 --> 00:39:33.520
Let the visitors be the judges.

00:39:34.200 --> 00:39:36.000
Then I can start preparing the exhibition.

00:39:36.560 --> 00:39:37.360
Wonderful.

00:39:37.360 --> 00:39:38.320
Go get it ready.

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:38.960
Okay.

00:40:00.040 --> 00:40:01.920
The effect is amazing.

00:40:02.120 --> 00:40:03.360
As long as you're satisfied.

00:40:03.960 --> 00:40:05.000
I have to say,

00:40:05.280 --> 00:40:08.000
When God didn't lend me a hand,

00:40:08.080 --> 00:40:10.680
It was you and Xuan paper that saved me.

00:40:10.880 --> 00:40:11.720
It's our pleasure.

00:40:12.040 --> 00:40:14.520
Many people were drawn in

00:40:14.520 --> 00:40:15.520
By the Xuan paper wallpaper.

00:40:15.720 --> 00:40:17.680
And they praised it highly.

00:40:18.000 --> 00:40:19.080
In the future,

00:40:19.160 --> 00:40:20.680
Not only my own designs

00:40:20.680 --> 00:40:23.680
Will incorporate Xuan paper elements,

00:40:23.800 --> 00:40:26.120
But I'll introduce all my peers

00:40:26.120 --> 00:40:27.520
To this amazing Xuan paper.

00:40:28.040 --> 00:40:29.400
That's wonderful, wonderful.

00:40:30.520 --> 00:40:33.280
Lin, we're about to become partners.

00:40:33.560 --> 00:40:35.040
Come, let me translate.

00:40:38.400 --> 00:40:40.040
Xuan Yi is so thoughtful.

00:40:43.000 --> 00:40:44.560
I have some relevant clients later,

00:40:44.560 --> 00:40:45.840
And I can introduce them to you.

00:40:45.840 --> 00:40:46.560
And then,

00:40:46.840 --> 00:40:48.640
They'll definitely be very interested.

00:40:49.000 --> 00:40:50.000
Thank you, Emma.

00:40:50.360 --> 00:40:51.560
Thank you, Mr. Riccardo.

00:40:51.560 --> 00:40:52.520
The trip was worth it.

00:40:52.680 --> 00:40:54.720
Xuan, you've shown me

00:40:54.720 --> 00:40:56.640
The mind of a Chinese designer.

00:40:56.720 --> 00:40:58.080
I just love you.

00:40:59.560 --> 00:41:01.920
Can we talk in more depth?

00:41:02.200 --> 00:41:03.280
Sure, sure, sure.

00:41:03.320 --> 00:41:04.360
That's way too enthusiastic.

00:41:04.800 --> 00:41:05.920
Come, this way, this way.

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:09.000
Come take a look at the effect.

00:41:09.640 --> 00:41:11.280
The mountains don't just have bamboo and potatoes,

00:41:11.280 --> 00:41:12.520
There are handsome guys too.

00:41:12.520 --> 00:41:15.440
He's not just handsome, he's thoughtful too.

00:41:15.520 --> 00:41:17.920
Not just thoughtful, but talented as well.

00:41:19.600 --> 00:41:21.400
The moment I saw him, I knew

00:41:21.400 --> 00:41:22.800
You're never coming back.

00:41:22.800 --> 00:41:23.800
Wishing you happiness.

00:41:24.000 --> 00:41:25.560
You're welcome to visit the mountains too.

00:41:25.640 --> 00:41:26.440
It's quite likely.

00:41:26.440 --> 00:41:28.360
Once you go, you won't want to come back either.

00:41:28.360 --> 00:41:29.160
I have to go.

00:41:35.280 --> 00:41:36.040
Great.

00:41:36.560 --> 00:41:37.000
Sure thing.

00:41:37.000 --> 00:41:38.200
However many orders you need,

00:41:38.200 --> 00:41:39.800
Just send them straight to me.

00:41:40.040 --> 00:41:40.440
Okay, okay.

00:41:40.440 --> 00:41:41.200
Thank you.

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:45.080
You really are a high-energy person.

00:41:45.280 --> 00:41:46.520
After such a long journey,

00:41:46.600 --> 00:41:47.920
You're still so full of energy.

00:41:48.520 --> 00:41:49.880
Alright, I did you such a big favor.

00:41:49.880 --> 00:41:51.640
Figured out how to thank me yet?

00:41:52.040 --> 00:41:52.840
Wait,

00:41:53.200 --> 00:41:54.520
Where did that come from?

00:41:54.520 --> 00:41:56.200
Wasn't it me who helped you?

00:41:56.560 --> 00:41:58.560
I didn't bring in orders for myself.

00:41:58.760 --> 00:42:00.600
It's for all Xuan paper businesses,

00:42:00.600 --> 00:42:02.040
Including yours.

00:42:02.480 --> 00:42:04.520
So you mean I have to thank you?

00:42:05.080 --> 00:42:05.880
A little louder.

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:08.040
I...

00:42:08.600 --> 00:42:10.840
Worked myself to death researching wallpaper,

00:42:11.280 --> 00:42:12.160
Spent all that labor and materials,

00:42:12.160 --> 00:42:13.360
Pulled all-nighters to make it for you,

00:42:13.360 --> 00:42:15.280
Even paid my own way to Beijing to deliver it,

00:42:15.280 --> 00:42:17.400
And in the end I have to thank you?

00:42:17.440 --> 00:42:19.880
Come on, is there any justice, boss?

00:42:19.880 --> 00:42:20.960
No justice.

00:42:20.960 --> 00:42:22.600
Hurry up and say thank you.

00:42:23.520 --> 00:42:26.760
Welcome, welcome, a warm welcome!

00:42:28.880 --> 00:42:30.160
Hello, you two.

00:42:30.640 --> 00:42:32.480
I'm Xiao, your private driver.

00:42:32.480 --> 00:42:33.800
Happy to be at your service.

00:42:33.800 --> 00:42:34.480
Come on.

00:42:34.800 --> 00:42:36.520
Wait, why did Chairman Xiao come himself?

00:42:37.040 --> 00:42:38.080
If I didn't pick you up in person,

00:42:38.080 --> 00:42:39.920
How could I show my gratitude?

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:41.160
Don't just be grateful.

00:42:41.160 --> 00:42:42.160
You owe us a dinner too.

00:42:42.160 --> 00:42:42.920
No problem.

00:42:43.200 --> 00:42:45.760
See? Someone's saying thanks for me.

00:42:45.800 --> 00:42:47.320
You and your little tricks.

00:42:47.680 --> 00:42:48.520
Get in.

00:42:49.040 --> 00:42:49.800
Princess, please get in.

00:42:49.800 --> 00:42:50.280
Watch your step.

00:42:50.280 --> 00:42:51.120
Get in, get in.

